&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Title&lt;/strong&gt;: Clinical Supervisor - Various Programs (see descriptions below)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Classification&lt;/strong&gt;: Regular Full Time and Part-Time options available&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location&lt;/strong&gt;: Oakland, CA / Hybrid&lt;/p&gt;
